This fix will handle some MP1 FW issue like as mclk dpm table in renoir has a reverse
dpm clock layout and a zero frequency dpm level as following case.

cat pp_dpm_mclk
0: 1200Mhz
1: 1200Mhz
2: 800Mhz
3: 0Mhz

